window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Taking her is my right. Breaking her, my duty.</p> <p>I was always going to choose Helena. I knew it the instant I saw her.</p> <p>She’s different than the others. There’s a darkness about her. Something wild inside her. And it calls to the beast inside me.</p> <p>But she isn’t what I expected. With every word and every touch, she pushes me, burrowing deep under my skin, challenging the rules, and upending history. </p> <p>And all the while, I see how my brother watches her. He wants her, and as the rules stand, she’ll become his in one year’s time.</p> <p>Except that I have no intention of giving her up. </p> <p><b>Author's Note:</b> <i>Torn</i> is the second and final audiobook of the Dark Legacy Duet.</p> <p><b><i>Contains mature themes.</i></b></p>"; 
